essed-1024x620.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-826\" width=\"512\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/1200px-Cadillac_Escalade_III_front-compressed-1024x620.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/1200px-Cadillac_Escalade_III_front-compressed-300x182.jpg 300w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/1200px-Cadillac_Escalade_III_front-compressed-768x465.jpg 768w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/1200px-Cadillac_Escalade_III_front-compressed-850x514.jpg 850w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/1200px-Cadillac_Escalade_III_front-compressed-24x15.jpg 24w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/1200px-Cadillac_Escalade_III_front-compressed-36x22.jpg 36w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/1200px-Cadillac_Escalade_III_front-compressed-48x29.jpg 48w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/1200px-Cadillac_Escalade_III_front-compressed.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Since its launch in 1999, the escalade has always been a beefy-looking, luxury cruiser. From the front of it, one can even mistake it for a pickup truck with the massive grille and huge ground clearance, but it is in all practicality a regular, high-end SUV.&nbsp; As of late, it is actually one of the biggest existing SUVs out there that weighs more than 3400-kilo grams with all the extra options.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"GMC_Hummer_EV_%E2%80%93_4103_kg\"><\/span>GMC Hummer EV &#8211; 4,103 kg<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"501\" src=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-1024x501.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-817\" srcset=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-1024x501.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-300x147.jpg 300w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-768x376.jpg 768w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-1536x752.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-850x416.jpg 850w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-24x12.jpg 24w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-36x18.jpg 36w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed-48x23.jpg 48w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/2024-GMC-HUMMER-EV-SUV-002-1-e1617562260895-compressed.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Up till now, Hummers have been quite the heavyweight in cars, so much so that they have become shorthand for big hulking IC vehicles. A few of them weigh over three and a half tons. But that certainly cannot be the end of it because you don&#x2019;t know heavy until you&#x2019;ve gone full electric! All the batteries and high-tech equipment increase weight quite significantly as have seen with some of the converted IC vehicles into EVs. And the all-new GMC Hummer EV is a real-life example of that. Its electric variant reportedly weighs in at an unbelievable 4,103-kilograms. Though fortunately, being electric, it will be faster than the older models &#8211; that&#x2019;s an upside.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mercedes-Benz_770_K_Cabriolet_Armored_4800_kg\"><\/span>Mercedes-Benz 770 K Cabriolet Armored 4800 kg<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed-1024x469.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-818\" width=\"512\" height=\"235\" srcset=\"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed-1024x469.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed-300x137.jpg 300w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed-768x351.jpg 768w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed-850x389.jpg 850w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed-24x11.jpg 24w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed-36x16.jpg 36w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed-48x22.jpg 48w, https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/tippco-934-fuehrerwagen-mit-hitler-und-3-soldaten-in-schwarz-compressed.jpg 1134w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You must have thought that this list would be topped by one of the Roll Royces or Bentleys, as they&#x2019;ve always been quite notoriously overweight. But there&#x2019;s another heavyweight around the block. The Mercedes-Benz 770 K Cabriolet Armored or Gro&#xDF;er Mercedes (German for The Great Mercedes). However, the thing that makes this car more interesting and imposing is its ties with Adolf Hitler and other Axis leaders. It was essentially a state vehicle used for government purposes.&nbsp; With extensive armor plating and an imposing design, it was used for rallies and coupes by the army and its heavy body is said to be comparable to a tank. It weighed in at 4800-kilo grams!.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Being heavy means being slow, and inefficient, and cumbersome, and if stuck in a puddle &#8211; Impossible to get out of. That&#x2019;s of course, talking about cars. But being heavy can also sometimes mean&#46;&#46;&#46;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":200024,"featured_media":812,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[19],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/810"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/200024"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=810"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/810\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":833,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/810\/revisions\/833"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/812"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=810"}],"wp:term":[{"taxo